{
  "__inputs": [{"name": "DS_PROMETHEUS", "label": "Prometheus", "description": "", "type": "datasource", "pluginId": "prometheus"}],
  "uid": "ruptura-overview",
  "title": "Ruptura — Workload Health",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "tags": ["ruptura"],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "datasource",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": false,
        "label": "Data Source",
        "options": [],
        "refresh": 1
      },
      {
        "name": "namespace",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": "${datasource}",
        "query": "label_values(ruptura_kpi{signal=\"health_score\"}, namespace)",
        "current": {"text": "All", "value": "$__all"},
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "refresh": 2,
        "label": "Namespace"
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "HealthScore per Workload",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "datasource": "${datasource}",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "ruptura_kpi{namespace=~\"$namespace\",signal=\"health_score\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{namespace}}/{{workload}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "min": 0, "max": 100, "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "red", "value": 0},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 40},
              {"color": "green", "value": 80}
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "showThresholdLabels": false}
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Stress + Fatigue",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 9, "x": 6, "y": 0},
      "datasource": "${datasource}",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "ruptura_kpi{namespace=~\"$namespace\",signal=\"stress\"}",
          "legendFormat": "stress {{workload}}"
        },
        {
          "expr": "ruptura_kpi{namespace=~\"$namespace\",signal=\"fatigue\"}",
          "legendFormat": "fatigue {{workload}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"min": 0, "max": 1}}
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Rupture Index",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 9, "x": 15, "y": 0},
      "datasource": "${datasource}",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rpt_rupture_index{namespace=~\"$namespace\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{host}}:{{metric}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": 0},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 1},
              {"color": "red", "value": 3}
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "colorMode": "background"}
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Anomaly Events",
      "type": "table",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8},
      "datasource": "${datasource}",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rpt_actions_total",
          "legendFormat": "{{actionType}}:{{tier}}:{{outcome}}",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {"showHeader": true}
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Action Queue",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Action Queue\n\nQuery active actions via the Ruptura REST API:\n\n```\nGET /api/v2/actions\n```\n\n**Tiers:**\n- **T1** — Auto-executed (confidence ≥ 0.85)\n- **T2** — Awaiting approval (confidence ≥ 0.60)\n- **T3** — Human-only (low confidence)\n\nApprove or reject T2 actions:\n```\nPOST /api/v2/actions/{id}/approve\nPOST /api/v2/actions/{id}/reject\n```"
      }
    }
  ],
  "time": {"from": "now-1h", "to": "now"}
}
